sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant GUI as PySide6 GUI
  participant Controller as AgentController
  participant Lifecycle
  participant Server
  participant Firewall
  User->>GUI: Click Start Agent
  GUI->>Controller: start_agent()
  Controller->>Lifecycle: initialize_components(config)
  alt Server URL configured
    Lifecycle->>Server: POST /api/agents/register (API Key)
    Server-->>Lifecycle: agent_id + JWT
    Lifecycle->>Server: GET /api/whitelist/agent-sync
    Server-->>Lifecycle: whitelist + versions
  else No server URL / unreachable
    Note over Lifecycle: record registration / whitelist_sync as degraded
  end
  Lifecycle->>Firewall: enable_whitelist_mode()
  Note over Lifecycle: log_sender / heartbeat_sender require server_url + agent_id;<br/>otherwise marked degraded
  Lifecycle-->>Controller: InitResult (ok | degraded | failed)
  alt overall == failed
    Controller-->>GUI: status_changed (error)
  else overall == degraded
    Controller-->>GUI: status_changed (degraded, issues=[...])
  else overall == ok
    Controller-->>GUI: status_changed (running)
  end
